quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  28,22,"Nde o fewrunoo telen Madyana, o maaki: Hino hasii ka Joomi am fewnirta lam, e laawol mo∆¥∆¥ol, hara mi majjataa e maggol."
  28,23,"Nde o hewtunoo ka …ìunndu Madyana, ndu …ìe yarnirta …óam, o tawi jamaa yim…ìe no yarna daabeeji mun, o tawi kadi rew…ìe …ói…óo, no jogitii dammi mun, habbii haa yim…ìe …ìen yarna. Annabi Muusaa maakani …ìe: Ko ha…ói on yarnidugol e yim…ìe …ìen? ∆Åe wi'i: Ko men woowti, ko martagol habboo, haa gaynaakoo…ìe …ìen pottoo; fii wata men jillondir e ma…ì…ìe, baaba amen, ko maw…óo nayeejo, o hippataa yarnugol, tawi bee men yarna menen, dammi amen …óin."
  28,24,"O yurmaa …ìe, o yarnani …ìe dammi ma…ì…ìe …óin. Refti o huccitiri ka …óowdi, fii fowtagol, o torii Joomi makko e ko o hatonjini, o maaki: Joomi am, min ko jippin…óaa e am woo e mo∆¥∆¥ere, ko mi hatonjin…óo."
  28,25,"Nde jiw…ìe …ìen hootunoo, …ìe humpiti …óum baaba ma…ì…ìe. O nuli kisan gooto e ma…ì…ìe, yo noddoy mo. Jiwo on ari mum, no yahra hersa, o wi'i: Baaba am no nodde, fii yo…ìugol ma njo…ìdi ko yarnan-…óaa men kon. Nde Muusaa hewtunoo ka maw…óo on, o humpiti mo fii makko, maw…óo on wallintini …ìernde makko, o wi'ani mo: wata a hulu, sabu a da…óii bone Fir'awna e yim…ìe mun too√±oo…ìe, tawde alaa ko …ìe waawani Madyana; …ìe hewtataa ma fes."
  28,26,"Gooto e jiw…ìe maw…óo on wi'i: ∆≥ettu mo ko aynane dammi, yo baaba. Tawde himo fotdiri e golle, sabu doole e nun…óal makko: si ko doole …óen, o wallitoray huuwude ko o halfinaa, hoolaare nden kan, ko ko reenira kon ko o halfinaa."
  28,27,"Ben ma…ì…ìe maakani Muusaa (yo …ìe his): Mi…óo yi…ói resindirde maa gooto e jiw…ìe am …ìen, nde te≈ãe makko …óen wonata aynangol lam dammi, duu…ìi jeetati. Si a timminii sappo, haray ko e sago maa, wa…ó…óaaki maa, tawde ko duu…ìi jeetati woni haldigal ngal, ko …ìeydii …óon woo, ko sago. Mi fonndaa …ìi…ótinirgol ma, ko sonnjata maa. A taway lam, si Alla ja…ìii, ko mi jeyaa…óo e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe, hunnoo…ìe ahadi, mo firtataa."
  28,28,"Muusaa maaki: ∆äum wonii ko fottan…óen, en …ói…óo. Kala happu mo mi timmini (woni duu…ìi jeetati …óin maa sappo), haray fow e mun, mi hunnii ko fawii lam kon; mi …óa…ì…ìiroytaake …ìeydugol. Alla ko Fawii…óo, Reenu…óo e ko haldu…óen kon."